The '''Prosslee''' were the former oppressors of the [[Forshul/Legends|Forshul]], a [[Species/Legends|species]] indigenous to the neighboring [[Yminis sector/Legends|Yminis sector]]. During the [[Caamas Document]] crisis, the Prosslee [[Senator/Legends|senator]] took a pro-[[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] stance in opposition to the Forshul. At least one Prosslee escort frigate participated in the [[Battle of Bothawui (Galactic Civil War)|Second Battle of Bothawui]], fighting first on behalf of the Bothans, and then as part of the united [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] fleet.

